<p>Chris Hughes, one of the founders of Facebook, [%
Ovid.cite('https://www.nytimes.com/2019/05/09/opinion/sunday/chris-hughes-facebook-zuckerberg.html',
'has called for it to be dismantled')%]. Needless to say this generated a ton
