<p>[%
Ovid.cite('https://www.vox.com/2014/6/30/11628448/flashing-back-to-2004-as-orkut-fades-away-a-decade-later',
"Vox has an interesting article about the mess that was Orkut" ) %], but it
basically amounts to a part-time project, written by Google employee Orkut
